English: His behavior is very contradictory, and I don't understand what he wants to do.

8. 吊詭 (似非而是、荒謬)

廣東話：佢講嘅話好吊詭，我都唔知佢係咪講真嘅。
English: What he says is very absurd, and I don't know if he is telling the truth.

9. 各為其主

廣東話：佢哋兩個人係各為其主，所以經常會有爭執。
English: They are both working for their own bosses, so they often have disagreements.

10. 軨蓋

廣東話：佢講嘅話好軨蓋，我都唔知佢係咪講真嘅。
