English: I went golfing with my friends yesterday and played many holes.

12. 免揀

廣東話：佢哋嘅貨品係免揀嘅，你只可以買佢哋有嘅。
English: Their products are sold without choice, and you can only buy what they have.

13. 擺闊佬

廣東話：佢好喜歡擺闊佬，經常諗住花錢。
English: He likes to show off his wealth and often thinks about spending money.

14. 廣播劇

廣東話：我尋日聽咗一套廣播劇，好好聽。
English: I listened to a radio drama yesterday, and it was very good.

15. 錄影機

